nbreak>11</unbreak>","vi":"Bí Ẩn Mạng <unbreak>11</unbreak>"},"part1":{"weakness_suggest":["Fire","Ice"],"totalWaves":2,"wave1":[{"monster_name":"Ichor Memosprite: Winged Serpent","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Ice"]},{"monster_name":"Senior Staff: Team Leader","monster_code":-1,"monster_weakness":["Fire","Ice","Imaginary"]}],"wave2":[{"monster_name":"Wonder Forest's Banacademic Office Staff","monster_code":4,"monster_weakness":["Fire","Ice","Thunder","Imaginary"]}]},"part2":{"weakness_suggest":["Physical","Imaginary"],"totalWaves":2,"wave1":[{"monster_name":"Dreamjolt Troupe's Sweet Gorilla","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Imaginary"]},{"monster_name":"Aurumaton Spectral Envoy","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Thunder","Imaginary"]}],"wave2":[{"monster_name":"Ichor Memosprite: Judge of Oblivion","monster_code":4,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Ice","Imaginary"]}]}},{"name":{"zh_cn":"网络谜踪其十二","zh_hk":"網路謎蹤其十二","de":"Netzwerkmysterium XII","en":"Cyber Mystery (XII)","es":"Misterio en la red XII","fr":"Cybermystère (XII)","id":"Misteri Siber <unbreak>12</unbreak>","jp":"サイバーミステリー・<unbreak>12</unbreak>","kr":"사이버 미스터리•<unbreak>12</unbreak>","pt":"Mistério Cibernético (XII)","ru":"Виртуальная тайна XII","th":"ปริศนาไซเบอร์ <unbreak>12</unbreak>","vi":"Bí Ẩn Mạng <unbreak>12</unbreak>"},"part1":{"weakness_suggest":["Fire"],"totalWaves":2,"wave1":[{"monster_name":"Rocking Rebel","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Wind"]},{"monster_name":"Canvas Peacock","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":[]},{"monster_name":"Aggressive Reading Material","monster_code":2,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Thunder"]}],"wave2":[{"monster_name":"@SparxiConOfficial","monster_code":4,"monster_weakness":["Fire","Quantum","Imaginary"]}]},"part2":{"weakness_suggest":["Physical","Wind"],"totalWaves":2,"wave1":[{"monster_name":"Lady of Crashing Waves","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Thunder"]},{"monster_name":"Black Tide's Corroded Daemon","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Wind","Quantum"]}],"wave2":[{"monster_name":"First Genius, Entelechy, Zandar","monster_code":4,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Ice","Wind"]}]}}],"name":{"zh_cn":"网络谜踪","zh_hk":"網路謎蹤","de":"Netzwerkmysterium","en":"Cyber Mystery","es":"Misterio en la red","fr":"Cybermystère","id":"Misteri Siber","jp":"サイバーミステリー","kr":"사이버 미스터리","pt":"Mistério Cibernético","ru":"Виртуальная тайна","th":"ปริศนาไซเบอร์","vi":"Bí Ẩn Mạng"},"desc":{"zh_cn":"每个波次或轮开始时，获得5个笑点，每次获得笑点时，为【记忆紊流】增加对应点数的充能，最多叠加50点。\\n每个轮开始时，【记忆紊流】根据充能点数对敌方目标造成1次真实伤害。","zh_hk":"每一波或每一輪開始時，獲得5個笑點，每次獲得笑點時，為【記憶紊流】增加對應點數的充能，最多疊加50點。\\n每一輪開始時，【記憶紊流】根據充能點數對敵方目標造成1次真實傷害。","de":"Erhält zu Beginn jeder Kampfwelle oder Runde 5 Lachpunkte. Jedes Mal, wenn Lachpunkte erhalten werden, wird eine entsprechende Anzahl an Aufladungen zu „Turbulenzen des Gedächtnisses“ hinzugefügt, bis zu 50 Pkt.\\nZu Beginn jeder Runde fügt „Turbulenzen des Gedächtnisses“ Gegnern basierend auf der Anzahl aufgeladener Punkte 1-mal Tatsächlichen SCH zu.","en":"At the start of each wave or Cycle, gains 5 Punchline point(s). When obtaining Punchline, adds a corresponding amount of Charge to \"Memory Turbulence,\" stacking up to 50 points.\\nAt the start of every Cycle, \"Memory Turbulence\" deals 1 instance of True DMG to enemy targets based on the amount of Charge points.","es":"Al comenzar cada oleada o ciclo, obtienes 5 puntos de Chiste. Cada vez que obtienes Chiste, la carga de Recuerdo turbulento aumenta en la misma cantidad, hasta un máximo de 50 puntos.\\nAl comenzar cada ciclo, Recuerdo turbulento inflige Daño verdadero una vez a los enemigos según los puntos de carga.","fr":"Au début de chaque vague ou cycle, accorde 5 point(s) de Panache. Chaque fois que du Panache est obtenu, le nombre correspondant de points de charge vient s'ajouter à la Turbulence mémorielle, jusqu'à un maximum de 50 points.\\nAu début de chaque cycle, la Turbulence mémorielle inflige 1 instance de DGT réels aux cibles ennemies en fonction des points de charge.","id":"Saat setiap gelombang atau putaran dimulai, memperoleh 5 Punchline. Setiap kali memperoleh Punchline, akan menambahkan Charge bagi \"Memory Turbulence\" sebesar poin tersebut, dapat ditumpuk hingga 50 poin.\\nSaat setiap putaran dimulai, \"Memory Turbulence\" akan mengakibatkan 1 kali True DMG berdasarkan poin Charge pada target musuh.","jp":"各ウェーブまたはラウンド開始時、爆笑ネタを5個を獲得する。爆笑ネタを獲得するたびに、獲得した数分、「記憶の乱流」をチャージする、最大で50までチャージできる。\\nラウンド開始時、「記憶の乱流」はチャージ数に応じて敵に確定ダメージを1回与える。","kr":"각 웨이브 또는 라운드가 시작될 때마다 웃음 포인트를 5pt 획득하며, 웃음 포인트를 획득할 때마다 획득한 포인트만큼 [기억의 와류]를 충전한다, 최대 중첩수: 50pt.\\n각 라운드가 시작될 때마다 [기억의 와류]는 충전 포인트에 따라 적에게 확정 피해를 1회 가한다","pt":"No início de cada onda ou Ciclo, ganha 5 ponto(s) de \"Piada\". Ao obter \"Piada\", adiciona a quantidade correspondente de Carga à \"Turbulência de Memória\", acumulando até 50 pontos.\\nNo início de cada Ciclo, a \"Turbulência de Memória\" causa 1 instância de <u>Dano Verdadeiro</u> aos inimigos-alvo com base na quantidade de pontos de Carga.","ru":"В начале каждой волны или цикла начисляется 5 ед. Юмора. Когда союзник получает единицы Юмора, он добавляет Турбулентности памяти до макс. 50 ед.\\nВ начале каждого цикла каждый удар Турбулентности памяти наносит цели истинный урон, равный количеству единиц энергии, 1 раз.","th":"เมื่อเริ่มต้นในแต่ละ Wave หรือรอบ จะได้รับจุดขำขัน 5 แต้ม ทุกครั้งที่ได้รับจุดขำขัน จะเพิ่มหน่วยชาร์จพลังให้กับ \"Memory Turbulence\" ในจำนวนที่สอดคล้องกัน โดยสามารถซ้อนทับได้สูงสุด 50 หน่วย\\nเมื่อเริ่มต้นในแต่ละรอบ \"Memory Turbulence\" จะสร้าง DMG จริง ให้แก่ศัตรูเป้าหมาย 1 ครั้ง ตามจำนวนหน่วยชาร์จพลัง","vi":"Khi bắt đầu mỗi đợt hoặc vòng, nhận được 5 Điểm Hài Hước, mỗi lần nhận Điểm Hài Hước sẽ tăng thêm điểm Nạp Năng Lượng tương ứng cho \"Dòng Hồi Ức Rối Loạn\", tối đa cộng dồn 50 điểm.\\nKhi bắt đầu mỗi vòng, \"Dòng Hồi Ức Rối Loạn\" sẽ gây 1 lần Sát Thương Chuẩn lên mục tiêu phe địch dựa theo số điểm Nạp Năng Lượng."},"time":{"begin":1772395200000,"end":1776024000000,"versionBegin":"4.0","versionEnd":"4.0"}}